Business Questions Answered
1. Which recruitment source produced the most successful hires?

SELECT
SOURCE,
COUNT(*) AS TOTAL_HIRES
FROM RECRUITMENT_SOURCE_EFFECTIVENESS
Insight: Jobs.ie produced the highest number of successful hires in the dataset.

2. Which account received the most hires?

SELECT
ACCOUNT,
COUNT(*) AS TOTAL_HIRES
FROM RECRUITMENT_SOURCE_EFFECTIVENESS
GROUP BY ACCOUNT
ORDER BY TOTAL_HIRES DESC;

